<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>BLESS THE LORD, O MY SOUL!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lal lopi chawian un, Amah mai Pathien,
 Chawian un, thilmak ei muhsak haw ziekin;
 Ei pautiem hi, I damsung khuolzin nau ah,
 Meikuong leh meipi-a ei pui pek dingin.

[V2]
 Angelhaw'n pakchau uo, Kingkang hawih tumin,
 A mite cheng chun Amah a chawian ui;
 A gam sung cheng achun kumsawt chan inle,
 A thilbawl cheng chengin (2)
 Chawian un au, aw, ka thagau, chawian un!

[V3]
 2. Chawian un, thagau saltangte A tandawk,
 Chawian un, damna tuikhuk A luonsak hi;
 Chawian un, A thilpiek leh venna ziekin,
 I paucham nau ei dawn ziekin chawian un.

[V4]
 3. Amah chuh chawian un, I lungkham unle,
 A hehpihnan A kawm ei naihsak ziekin;
 Ginna leh kinepna ziekin chawian un,
 A gam nuomah lungdeih te kituok khawm ding.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>445</hymn_number>
</song>